OL,3,CYouth speeding on the rise in Jersey
OL,5,FSo far this year, Jersey police have
OL,6,Fissued more than a hundred tickets to
OL,7,Fspeeding drivers under the age of 25,
OL,8,Fsurpassing the 114 tickets issued in
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FITV News went out with St Brelade
OL,12,FHonoraries to see first hand the
OL,13,Fextent of the problem.
OL,15,FOur reporter witnessed one motorist
OL,16,Fdriving down the Five Mile Road in
OL,17,FJersey at 78 miles per hour, and
OL,18,Fanother doing 73 miles per hour.
