OL,3,CYouth speeding on the rise in Jersey
OL,5,FMichel Bougeard said: "Without the
OL,6,FHonorary Police, the States Police
OL,7,Fcouldn't cope and they've said that
OL,8,Fthemselves.
OL,10,F"They would have to get more officers
OL,11,Fwhich would mean they would have to
OL,12,Fpay more which would mean taxes would
OL,13,Fgo up."
